      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Miroslav Kubat</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"http://www.coe.miami.edu/faculty-directory/name/miroslav-kubat/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/36/Mroslavkubat.jpg/240px-Mroslavkubat.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/3/36/Mroslavkubat.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Mroslavkubat.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Miroslav Kubat <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Miroslav Kubat</b>,<br />\na Czech American computer scientist and associate professor at Department of Electrical and Computer Engineering, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Miami\">University of Miami</a> and before,  ssociate professor in CS at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Louisiana_at_Lafayette\">University of Louisiana at Lafayette</a>. His research focuses on <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">machine learning</a>, <a href=\"/Neural_Networks\" title=\"Neural Networks\">neural networks</a>, and <a href=\"/Pattern_Recognition\" title=\"Pattern Recognition\">pattern recognition</a>. \nPrior to coming to the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States\">U.S</a>, he held positions in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Austria\">Austria</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Canada\">Canada</a>, and the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Czech_Republic\">Czech Republic</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1990_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1990 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Miroslav_Kubat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1990_...\">1990 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Miroslav_Kubat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1990 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miroslav Kubat</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i>Introduction to Machine Learning</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/ac/ai1992.html\">Advanced Topics in Artificial Intelligence 1992</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miroslav Kubat</a> (<b>1996</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Second-Tier-for-Decision-Trees-Kubat/b6197c531b1c83dfaa52563449f9b8248cc68c5a\">Second Tier for Decision Trees</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/icml/icml1996.html#Kubat96\">ICML 1996</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miroslav Kubat</a>, <a href=\"/Robert_Holte\" title=\"Robert Holte\">Robert Holte</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#SMatwin\" title=\"Mathematician\">Stan Matwin</a> (<b>1997</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-62858-4_79\">Learning When Negative Examples Abound</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/ecml/ecml97.html\">ECML 1997</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miroslav Kubat</a>, <a href=\"/Robert_Holte\" title=\"Robert Holte\">Robert Holte</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#SMatwin\" title=\"Mathematician\">Stan Matwin</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1023/A:1007452223027\">Machine Learning for the Detection of Oil Spills in Satellite Radar Images</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Machine_Learning_(journal)\">Machine Learning</a>, Vol. 30</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ryszard_Michalski\" title=\"Ryszard Michalski\">Ryszard Michalski</a>, <a href=\"/Ivan_Bratko\" title=\"Ivan Bratko\">Ivan Bratko</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miroslav Kubat</a> (eds.) (<b>1998</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.wiley.com/en-gb/Machine+Learning+and+Data+Mining%3A+Methods+and+Applications-p-9780471971993\">Machine Learning and Data Mining: Methods and Applications</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Wiley_%26_Sons\">John Wiley &amp; Sons</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miroslav Kubat</a>, <a href=\"/Ivan_Bratko\" title=\"Ivan Bratko\">Ivan Bratko</a>, <a href=\"/Ryszard_Michalski\" title=\"Ryszard Michalski\">Ryszard Michalski</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i>A Review of Machine Learning Methods</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://lacam.di.uniba.it/people/courses/IA/IA1213/IA/letture/MLReview.pdf\">pdf</a></dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Miroslav_Kubat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miroslav Kubat</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan_%C5%BDi%C5%BEka&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jan Žižka (page does not exist)\">Jan Žižka</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F3-540-45049-1_52\">Learning Middle Game Patterns in Chess: A Case Study</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lecture_Notes_in_Computer_Science\">Lecture Notes in Computer Science</a>, Vol. 1821, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miroslav Kubat</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://journals.cambridge.org/action/displayAbstract?fromPage=online&amp;aid=58577\">Designing neural network architectures for pattern recognition</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dblp2.uni-trier.de/db/journals/ker/ker15.html\">The Knowledge Engineering Review, Vol. 15</a>, No. 2</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Johannes_F%C3%BCrnkranz\" title=\"Johannes Fürnkranz\">Johannes Fürnkranz</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miroslav Kubat</a> (eds.) (<b>2001</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.novapublishers.org/catalog/product_info.php?products_id=720\">Machines that Learn to Play Games</a></i>. Advances in Computation: Theory and Practice, Vol. 8,. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nova_Publishers\">NOVA Science Publishers</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Miroslav_Kubat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/q/Quirino:Thiago\">Thiago Quirino</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miroslav Kubat</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/b/Bryan:Nicholas_J=\">Nicholas J. Bryan</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.computer.org/csdl/trans/tk/2010/12/ttk2010121724.html\">Instinct-Based Mating in Genetic Algorithms Applied to the Tuning of 1-NN Classifiers</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TKDE\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Knowledge and Data Engineering</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miroslav Kubat</a> (<b>2015</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.springer.com/us/book/9783319348865#otherversion=9783319200095\">An Introduction to Machine Learning</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a> </li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miroslav Kubat</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.springer.com/gp/book/9783319639123\">An Introduction to Machine Learning</a></i>. Second Edition, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/d/Dhrif:Hassen\">Hassen Dhrif</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/g/Giraldo:Luis_G=_S=eacute=nchez\">Luis G. Sanchez Giraldo</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miroslav Kubat</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.wuchtylab.org/\">Stefan Wuchty</a> (<b>2019</b>). <i>A Stable Combinatorial Particle Swarm Optimization for Scalable Feature Selection in Gene Expression Data</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1901.08619\">arXiv:1901.08619</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Miroslav_Kubat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.coe.miami.edu/faculty-directory/name/miroslav-kubat/\">Miroslav Kubat | People Directory | UM COE</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ijcai.org/past/ijcai-01/tutorial_program.htm#SA3\">IJCAI tutorial program for 2001 - Neural Networks for Pattern Recognition: The Impact of Architecture</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miroslav Kubat</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ots.at/presseaussendung/OTS_20130612_OTS0255/vortrag-profdr-miroslav-kubat-multi-label-hierarchical-classification\">VORTRAG: Prof.Dr. Miroslav Kubat \"MULTI-LABEL HIERARCHICAL CLASSIFICATION\" | Österreichische Studiengesellschaft für Kybernetik, 12.06.2013</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Miroslav_Kubat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.coe.miami.edu/faculty-directory/name/miroslav-kubat/\">Miroslav Kubat | People Directory | UM COE</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ijcai.org/past/ijcai-01/tutorial_program.htm#SA3\">IJCAI tutorial program for 2001 - Neural Networks for Pattern Recognition: The Impact of Architecture</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Miroslav Kubat</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/k/Kubat:Miroslav\">dblp: Miroslav Kubat</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228212432\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.020 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.021 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 69/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 142/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 by